Please follow the below steps to make an Aloo Tikki:

1) Take boiled potatoes.
2) Add some chopped mint leaves and green chillies.
3) Add some lemon juice.
4) Add some normal salt and black salt to taste.
5) Add some rice flour for binding.
6) Make a dough from the mixture.
7) Make small patties.
7) shallow fry the patties.
-----------------
Ready to serve!! :D
Thank you!
